                WebServiceFeature</link></para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
                <para><link
                xlink:href="http://jax-ws-architecture-document.java.net/nonav/doc21/jax-ws-ri-overview?com/sun/xml/ws/api/server/package-summary.html">Hosting
                API</link> <itemizedlist>
